                            </strong>          </td>
                                                                                        <td headers="view-body-table-column" class="views-field views-field-body">Duke students can receive credit for courses taken at UNC-Chapel Hill, UNC-Charlotte, or UNC-Greensboro, NC Central University, or NC State University. You can only do this if you are a full-time student and if the equivalent course is not being offered at Duke during the same academic term.          </td>
              </tr>
